		text		: "1\n00:00:16,817 --> 00:00:20,437\nHi!\n\n2\n00:00:20,540 --> 00:00:23,460\nToday, my friend Ashley, is coming over.\n\n3\n00:00:23,762 --> 00:00:26,285\nI am showing her my new apartment!\n\n4\n00:00:26,487 --> 00:00:29,913\nOh! That’s Ashley calling.\n\n5\n00:00:30,524 --> 00:00:32,637\nHi Ashley!\n\n6\n00:00:32,738 --> 00:00:33,744\nHi Anna!\n\n7\n00:00:33,947 --> 00:00:35,358\nI’m coming to your apartment.\n\n8\n00:00:35,458 --> 00:00:37,371\nWhere is your apartment?\n\n9\n00:00:37,576 --> 00:00:41,200\nMy apartment is near the Columbia Heights Metro.\n\n10\n00:01:18,460 --> 00:01:21,478\nIt is near the Columbia Heights Metro?\n\n11\n00:01:21,578 --> 00:01:24,294\nYes. Exit the Metro and turn right.\n\n12\n00:01:24,497 --> 00:01:27,316\nThen at the bus station turn left.\n\n13\n00:01:27,518 --> 00:01:29,227\nThen walk straight ahead.\n\n14\n00:02:18,545 --> 00:02:20,559\nOkay.\n\n15\n00:02:20,962 --> 00:02:25,702\nExit Metro, turn right, turn left, then go straight ahead?\n\n16\n00:02:26,007 --> 00:02:29,839\nYes. My apartment is near a coffee shop.\n\n17\n00:02:29,942 --> 00:02:31,860\nOkay. See you soon!\n\n18\n00:02:35,845 --> 00:02:36,753\nHi, Ashley.\n\n19\n00:02:36,853 --> 00:02:38,670\nHello. Anna, Which coffee shop?\n\n20\n00:02:38,794 --> 00:02:41,004\nThere are three coffee shops.\n\n21\n00:02:41,306 --> 00:02:46,038\nOkay, my apartment is across from a big department store.\n\n22\n00:02:46,248 --> 00:02:47,859\nA big department store?\n\n23\n00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:49,873\nAh, I see it!\n\n24\n00:02:50,181 --> 00:02:51,303\nOkay! Bye, Ashley.\n\n25\n00:02:51,404 --> 00:02:52,109\nSee you soon!\n\n26\n00:02:52,621 --> 00:02:54,233\nOkay. See you soon.\n\n27\n00:03:00,105 --> 00:03:04,139\nAshley! Ashley! Ashley!\n\n28\n00:03:04,537 --> 00:03:05,539\nOver here!\n\n29\n00:03:05,849 --> 00:03:09,068\nIt’s Anna! It’s Anna! Hi!\n\n30\n00:03:12,175 --> 00:03:14,704\nI love having my friends over.\n\n31\n00:03:15,114 --> 00:03:16,419\nCome on!\n\n32\n00:03:17,626 --> 00:03:17,626\nGreat!\n\n33\n00:03:26,478 --> 00:03:27,484\nHi!\n\n34\n00:03:27,685 --> 00:03:30,603\nToday, my friend Ashley, is coming over.\n\n35\n00:03:31,309 --> 00:03:33,222\nI am showing her my new apartment!\n\n36\n00:03:34,128 --> 00:03:36,846\nOh! That’s Ashley calling.\n\n37\n00:03:37,451 --> 00:03:39,562\nHi Ashley!\n\n38\n00:03:39,863 --> 00:03:40,868\nHi Anna!\n\n39\n00:03:40,974 --> 00:03:42,284\nI’m coming to your apartment.\n\n40\n00:03:42,586 --> 00:03:44,301\nWhere is your apartment?\n\n41\n00:03:44,628 --> 00:03:48,156\nMy apartment is near the Columbia Heights Metro.\n\n42\n00:03:48,458 --> 00:03:50,975\nIt is near the Columbia Heights Metro?\n\n43\n00:03:51,178 --> 00:03:53,897\nYes. Exit the Metro and turn right.\n\n44\n00:03:54,098 --> 00:03:56,813\nThen at the bus station turn left.\n\n45\n00:03:57,016 --> 00:03:58,925\nThen walk straight ahead.\n\n46\n00:03:59,027 --> 00:04:00,235\nOkay.\n\n47\n00:04:00,444 --> 00:04:04,777\nExit Metro, turn right, turn left, then go straight ahead?\n\n48\n00:04:04,886 --> 00:04:08,952\nYes. My apartment is near a coffee shop.\n\n49\n00:04:09,165 --> 00:04:10,877\nOkay. See you soon!\n\n50\n00:04:13,972 --> 00:04:15,381\nHi, Ashley.\n\n51\n00:04:15,584 --> 00:04:17,599\nHello. Anna, Which coffee shop?\n\n52\n00:04:17,706 --> 00:04:19,623\nThere are three coffee shops.\n\n53\n00:04:19,724 --> 00:04:24,656\nOkay, my apartment is across from a big department store.\n\n54\n00:04:24,780 --> 00:04:26,694\nA big department store?\n\n55\n00:04:27,106 --> 00:04:28,615\nAh, I see it!\n\n56\n00:04:28,923 --> 00:04:30,029\nOkay! Bye, Ashley.\n\n57\n00:04:30,239 --> 00:04:31,044\nSee you soon!\n\n58\n00:04:31,456 --> 00:04:32,965\nOkay. See you soon.\n\n59\n00:04:39,512 --> 00:04:42,933\nAshley! Ashley! Ashley!\n\n60\n00:04:43,359 --> 00:04:44,375\nOver here!\n\n61\n00:04:44,778 --> 00:04:47,896\nIt’s Anna! It’s Anna! Hi!\n\n62\n00:04:50,693 --> 00:04:53,550\nI love having my friends over.\n\n63\n00:04:53,852 --> 00:04:55,261\nCome on!\n\n64\n00:04:55,471 --> 00:04:56,375\nGreat!",
