		title		: "Lesson 17: Are You Free on Friday?",
		text		: "1\n00:00:24,429 --> 00:00:26,349\nHi, there!\n\n2\n00:00:26,550 --> 00:00:29,863\nThings are going really well in Washangton, D.C.\n\n3\n00:00:30,089 --> 00:00:32,220\nThis city is very interesting,\n\n4\n00:00:32,511 --> 00:00:33,919\nI really like my job,\n\n5\n00:00:34,120 --> 00:00:36,134\nand I have some good friends!\n\n6\n00:00:37,040 --> 00:00:40,871\nSpeaking of friends … I see one now! Marsha! Hi!\n\n7\n00:00:41,179 --> 00:00:43,195\nHi, Anna. What’s going on?\n\n8\n00:00:43,499 --> 00:00:45,414\nNot much. How about you?\n\n9\n00:00:45,515 --> 00:00:46,723\nBusy as usual.\n\n10\n00:00:47,025 --> 00:00:49,745\nHey, do you wanna see a movie with me?\n\n11\n00:00:49,951 --> 00:00:54,894\nSure! I never have time to see a movie. When?\n\n12\n00:00:55,203 --> 00:00:58,023\nAre you busy this Thursday at 6pm?\n\n13\n00:00:58,856 --> 00:01:00,397\nLet’s see ….\n\n14\n00:01:02,513 --> 00:01:03,420\nI’m busy.\n\n15\n00:01:03,731 --> 00:01:07,459\nI am going to tap dance with my friends Thursday night.\n\n16\n00:01:07,860 --> 00:01:08,766\nTap dancing?\n\n17\n00:01:08,966 --> 00:01:10,075\nThat sounds fun!\n\n18\n00:01:10,275 --> 00:01:11,583\nI’m still learning.\n\n19\n00:01:11,885 --> 00:01:12,893\nBut it is fun!\n\n20\n00:02:11,547 --> 00:02:13,664\nAre you busy on Friday night?\n\n21\n00:02:13,866 --> 00:02:18,195\nYes. Friday nights are when I visit my parents.\n\n22\n00:02:18,406 --> 00:02:20,622\nWhat do you and your family do together?\n\n23\n00:02:20,832 --> 00:02:25,564\nWe always eat dinner together and sometimes we play board games.\n\n24\n00:02:25,774 --> 00:02:27,801\nPlaying board games is fun, too!\n\n25\n00:02:28,009 --> 00:02:31,247\nThe word game Scrabble is my favorite.\n\n26\n00:02:31,574 --> 00:02:33,486\nI like Connect Four!\n\n27\n00:02:45,401 --> 00:02:48,117\nI’m not busy Monday night. Are you?\n\n28\n00:02:48,333 --> 00:02:50,750\nI am busy on Monday night.\n\n29\n00:02:51,067 --> 00:02:54,083\nI’m going to jog in the park with my friend.\n\n30\n00:02:54,391 --> 00:02:55,999\nDo you jog?\n\n31\n00:02:56,347 --> 00:02:58,272\nOh! I always jog.\n\n32\n00:02:58,704 --> 00:03:01,121\nWell, sometimes I jog.\n\n33\n00:03:02,953 --> 00:03:04,160\nOkay, I never jog.\n\n34\n00:03:04,676 --> 00:03:08,701\nBut I will try because it is good for you.\n\n35\n00:03:09,326 --> 00:03:12,244\nI always feel great after I jog.\n\n36\n00:03:44,096 --> 00:03:46,109\nHow about on Wednesday night?\n\n37\n00:03:46,423 --> 00:03:48,537\nWednesday night I am not busy.\n\n38\n00:03:48,657 --> 00:03:50,065\nOh, no, wait.\n\n39\n00:03:50,291 --> 00:03:53,015\nThis Wednesday night I will be busy.\n\n40\n00:03:53,333 --> 00:03:54,642\nWhat are you doing?\n\n41\n00:03:55,063 --> 00:03:58,484\nI’m going to teach children how to play the ukulele.\n\n42\n00:03:58,813 --> 00:04:09,491\nNow, children, play “C.” Good. I like your “C.”\n\n43\n00:04:11,228 --> 00:04:13,955\nThe world does need more ukulele players.\n\n44\n00:04:14,158 --> 00:04:19,798\nMarsha, it looks like we’ll never have time to see a movie.\n\n45\n00:04:20,602 --> 00:04:22,316\nWait a minute.\n\n46\n00:04:22,722 --> 00:04:24,139\nAre you busy now?\n\n47\n00:04:24,456 --> 00:04:26,872\nIt’s Saturday afternoon.\n\n48\n00:04:27,290 --> 00:04:29,810\nThis is always when I do my errands.\n\n49\n00:04:30,251 --> 00:04:35,583\nOkay, but the new Star Wars movie is gonna start in 30 minutes.\n\n50\n00:04:35,998 --> 00:04:38,213\nI’ll do my errands on Sunday.\n\n51\n00:04:38,534 --> 00:04:39,641\nLet’s go!\n\n52\n00:04:43,977 --> 00:04:47,602\nMost days of the week, people are really busy.\n\n53\n00:04:47,905 --> 00:04:51,528\nBut it’s important to find time to be with your friends!\n\n54\n00:04:51,930 --> 00:04:53,343\nUntil next time!\n\n55\n00:04:54,892 --> 00:04:58,821\n* Connect Four is a two-player connection game using colored discs.",
